Package es.utils.mapper.factory Description

Provides a set of factory classes to help the user to create custom mappings.
The package contains the following factories:
  • CollectionFactory : for creatinga collection based on destination class type
  • ElementMapperFactory : for creating an ElementMapper based on input and output values
  • GetterFactory : for creating an Getter based on input values
  • SetterFactory : for creating an setter based on output values
Author:
eschoysman
See Also:
CollectionFactory, ElementMapperFactory, GetterFactory, SetterFactory
